Our products & brandsExxonMobil Fuels & Lubricants (F&L) offers some of the most recognized lubricants brands worldwide, known for performance and innovation, respected and relied upon by consumers and businesses alike.Passenger Vehicle LubricantsMobil 1™ — For outstanding automotive drivingThe world’s leading synthetic motor oil brand, Mobil 1, is engineered to perform and protect under some of the most demanding conditions on the planet. Mobil 1 is among the leaders in motorsports and chosen for factory-fill by more auto manufacturers than any other motor oil brand.Commercial Vehicle LubricantsMobil Delvac 1™ and Mobil Delvac™— heavy-duty lubricants for commercial vehiclesExxonMobil has specialized in heavy-duty lubricants for more than 80 years. Year after year, decade after decade, Owner/Operators and fleets continue to put their trust in Mobil Delvac 1™ and Mobil Delvac™ lubricants to meet their protection and fuel economy needs.Mobil™ Industrial LubricantsMaking plant and machinery productivity flyFor over 100 years, we have established an unsurpassed reputation as a supplier of leading-edge lubricants with in-depth industry expertise, programs, and tools to help bring customers to new heights of equipment productivity. Learn how we can help your productivity take off.ExxonMobil Marine LubricantsProtecting the engines and equipment of some of the world's most important fleetsAs a leading supplier of marine lubricants, we can help your fleet operate more efficiently and cost effectively. Let us show you how.ExxonMobil Aviation LubricantsAdvanced lubricant technology for commercial and general aviationWe offer the latest-generation synthetic turbine oils, hydraulic fluids, and aviation greases for commercial aviation customers. We also provide a portfolio of products to general aviation customers.ExxonMobil Base StocksReliable supply of consistent quality lubricant base stocksAs one of the world's largest suppliers of base stocks, ExxonMobil strives to bring the most efficient production capacity to the marketplace -- offering products that help enable performance and excellence for virtually all lubricants.ExxonMobil White Oil & WaxWe are one of the largest global suppliers of wax and white oilOur commitment to product quality, availability, and reliability will help you realize supply chain efficiencies and operate with confidence.ExxonMobil Asphalt (Bitumen)ExxonMobil Fuels & Lubricants is among the world’s leading producers and marketers of asphalt (bitumen)We ensure consistent product quality by use of approved feedstock, tight control of manufacturing conditions, and extensive product testing. 













