                                Jobs & careers
                                













Careers and workforce  


    A dynamic and exciting place to work.

Hiring, developing and retaining a highly talented and diverse workforce

    Our greatest strength is the exceptional quality of our employees. The combined talents of our diverse workforce make ExxonMobil more competitive, more resilient and better able to navigate the complex and constantly changing global energy business. Our employees thrive on change, new technology and synergistic partnerships both inside and outside our company.

Careers at ExxonMobil

    ExxonMobil is a dynamic, exciting place to work. We hire exceptional people, and every one of them is empowered to think independently, to take initiative and be innovative. At ExxonMobil, you can expect to be apart of a highly productive work environment that treats all employees with respect, values diverse perspectives, encourages individual growth and achievement and rewards people based on their performance.

Explore U.S. careers > 

Search for global careers >

To apply for a job at an Exxon or Mobil station, please contact the local Station Manager directly. Use our Fuel Finder to find a station and obtain the address and phone number.







Fostering a collaborative, supportive and productive work environment


    ExxonMobil is committed to our employees’ professional development and supporting their career goals. We strive to provide an environment where personal and professional growth is encouraged and career objectives are developed and achieved.

Tools and processes for development include:


Annual performance assessments where employees have a structured, documented discussion about work accomplishments, training objectives, growth opportunities and career interests
Professional and technical training programs and leadership development programs and mentorships
Comprehensive employee benefits






    Already part of the ExxonMobil team?

Click here for employee practices and policies >


Are you an Exxon or Mobil Station Manager?

Click here to access the resource center >













