                                Consumer credit card
                                















Sign up for 2 months of extra savings

    Enjoy a smarter and more convenient way to save.








Sign up for 2 months of extra savings

Get 20¢ off every gallon* of Synergy™ gasoline at Exxon™ or Mobil™ stations for the first 2 months after your account open date with the ExxonMobil Smart Card. Offer ends August 31, 2017.

Then, get 6¢ off every gallon* of Synergy gasoline every day, at over 11,000 Exxon and Mobil stations. Plus, get 2X Plenti points at the pump.
You can earn 1 Plenti point and 1 additional point on each gallon of Synergy gasoline you purchase using your ExxonMobil Smart Card now through December 31, 2017. Extra Plenti points will be added to your Plenti account as bonus points.
Now you can apply for, and start paying with, the ExxonMobil Smart Card through the Speedpass+ app .
Flexible payment terms – choose a billing date that’s convenient for you.
Track fuel costs – an easy-to-read monthly statement itemizes your purchases.
Enjoy ATM cash access with your Smart Card (cash advance fees apply).
Citi® Identity Theft Solutions – enjoy peace of mind.
$0 Fraud liability – feel secure with $0 liability on unauthorized charges.



      Apply today!
    













                                    Refuel car. Reward self.
                                    
                                

                                    Earn 2,000 bonus Plenti® points, worth at least $20 in savings, † when you use the Speedpass+™ app to pay for 3 fill-ups of 10 gallons or more. Terms apply.

